# c1
> claude.max
< tokens <= 50000
@forward c2
@file -markdown risk_notes.md

Review the attached contract.
Identify obligations, termination rights, payment risks, confidentiality constraints, and clauses that need legal review.
Write the output as concise notes with section references.

# c2
> openai.fast
@forward c3
@text <800

Turn %from c1 into a negotiation checklist.
Separate must-change items from acceptable risks.

# c3
> (claude + openai).best
@file -markdown redline_brief.md

Use %from c1 and %from c2 to produce a final redline brief.
Keep it factual and avoid inventing missing contract language.
